  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Groundfall is a minimalist sandbox game where you fly bush airplanes in an open wilderness setting!  Attempt to take-off and land your STOL airplane at rugged and remote locations as you complete missions to explore, camp, build, survive, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly aerial missions while working to keep yourself and your airplane in one piece.  When you're not flying, you'll be busy surviving! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.poster.avif?t=1745775969\" width=798 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.webm?t=1745775969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.mp4?t=1745775969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/cbbb41f15d45498fc641b2d22dc179a6.avif?t=1745775969\" width=600 height=75 /></span><strong>Flight Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based Flight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airplane Damage/repair System </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airplane Fueling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flaps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water Assisted Landings (hydro-plane) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrain-based Friction (wet grass, mud, snow, ice) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival & Crafting Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple weapons, tools, and resources can be crafted, found, or unlocked</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft primitive tools and weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build Campsites, Shelters, Cabins, and even  Runways </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather, harvest, and hunt food and other resources to manage energy, hunger, and thirst  (optional)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environmental Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world maps and missions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lush ground vegetation and trees </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simulated seasonal weather with rain, snow, lightning </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Volumetric fog/clouds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI wildlife</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GroundFall is in constant development, future updates will included new maps, improvements, mission objectives, and more  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Groundfall is a minimalist sandbox game where you fly bush airplanes in an open wilderness setting!  Attempt to take-off and land your STOL airplane at rugged and remote locations as you complete missions to explore, camp, build, survive, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly aerial missions while working to keep yourself and your airplane in one piece.  When you're not flying, you'll be busy surviving! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.poster.avif?t=1745775969\" width=798 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.webm?t=1745775969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/0573d628585926331b8ec9db1d0426a1.mp4?t=1745775969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/934260/extras/cbbb41f15d45498fc641b2d22dc179a6.avif?t=1745775969\" width=600 height=75 /></span><strong>Flight Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based Flight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airplane Damage/repair System </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airplane Fueling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flaps </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water Assisted Landings (hydro-plane) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrain-based Friction (wet grass, mud, snow, ice) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival & Crafting Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple weapons, tools, and resources can be crafted, found, or unlocked</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft primitive tools and weapons </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build Campsites, Shelters, Cabins, and even  Runways </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather, harvest, and hunt food and other resources to manage energy, hunger, and thirst  (optional)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Environmental Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world maps and missions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lush ground vegetation and trees </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simulated seasonal weather with rain, snow, lightning </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Volumetric fog/clouds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI wildlife</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GroundFall is in constant development, future updates will included new maps, improvements, mission objectives, and more  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
